These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: radish, grapes
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, dahlia
1. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food   | radish  | grapes |
| Flower     | dahlia | begonia  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
House: craftsman, palace
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, blues
1. the palace house is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| House    | craftsman      | palace         |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | blues |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, prince
1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Pet   | chinchilla | hamster   |
| Cigar       | prince  | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
City: paris, edinburgh
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, fisherman
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| City   | paris  | edinburgh |
| Job         | architect | fisherman    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
