.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-8::.
City: boston, new-york
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, writing
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |
| City   | new-york     | boston   |
| Hobby        | skydiving | writing |

